ple.com/hook\""}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-border px-4 py-2 break-words min-w-[100px]","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"prompt"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-border px-4 py-2 break-words min-w-[100px]","children":"注入额外 prompt 给 Claude"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-border px-4 py-2 break-words min-w-[100px]","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"\"prompt\": \"记得检查类型安全\""}]}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-border px-4 py-2 break-words min-w-[100px]","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"agent"}]}],["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-border px-4 py-2 break-words min-w-[100px]","children":"启动一个子代理处理"}],["$","td",null,{"className":"border border-border px-4 py-2 break-words min-w-[100px]","children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"\"agent\": \"security-checker\""}]}]]}]]}]]}]}]
87:["$","h3",null,{"id":"44-配置格式","className":"text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-2 scroll-mt-24","children":"4.4 配置格式"}]
88:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["Hooks 配置在 settings.json 中，采用",["$","strong",null,{"children":"嵌套结构"}],"——每个事件下是一组匹配规则，每条规则包含一个 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"matcher"}],"（可选）和对应的 ",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"hooks"}]," 数组："]}]
89:["$","$L1b4",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"PreToolUse\": [\n      {\n        \"matcher\": \"Write\",\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"command\",\n            \"command\": \"node ./scripts/pre-tool-check.js\",\n            \"timeout\": 5\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"SessionStart\": [\n      {\n        \"hooks\": [\n          {\n            \"type\": \"prompt\",\n            \"prompt\": \"请先阅读 CHANGELOG.md 了解最近的变更\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n"}]}]
8a:["$","p",null,{"className":"my-4 leading-relaxed break-words","children":["注意结构层次：",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"hooks → 事件名 → [ { matcher?, hooks: [...] } ]"}],"。",["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"matcher"}]," 不填则匹配该事件的所有触发。"]}]
8b:["$","$L1b4",null,{"children":["$","code",null,{"className":"bg-muted text-slate-800 dark:text-foreground px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded text-sm font-normal font-mono break-all","children":"\n### 4.5 过滤机制：matcher 与 if\n\n- **`matcher`**：正则表达式，匹配工具名（如 `Write`、`Bash`）。对于工具相关事件（`PreToolUse` / `PostToolUse`），`matcher` 匹配的是工具名称\n- **`if`**：使用**权限规则语法**（permission rule syntax），如 `Bash(npm test)`、`Write(src/**)`，而非 JavaScript 表达式\n\n两者同时配置时，必须**同时满足**才会触发。\n\n### 4.6 退出码与决策控制\n\nHook 脚本的退出码决定了后续行为：\n\n| 退出码 | 含义 | 行为 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| **0** | 成功 | 继续执行，处理 stdout 中的 JSON 输出 |\n| **2** | 阻断错误 | 中止操作，将 stderr 内容反馈给 Claude |\n| **其他** | 非阻断错误 | 记录警告，继续执行 |\n\n**决策控制 JSON**（通过 stdout 返回）：\n\n对于 `PreToolUse` 事件，Hook 可通过 JSON 输出控制工具调用：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"permissionDecision\": \"allow\"\n}\n"}]}]
